{"title":"沙河谣","authors":["袁同兴"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙河谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁同兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙河流水长又长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前两岸白茫茫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大大小小沙滩地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菅草、谷莠都不长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙河流水弯又弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸村庄遭水淹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十有九年涨大水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户哭翻天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙河流水长又长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今庄稼青堂堂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连成大块水田地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种麦、种稻、种高粱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙河流水弯又弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸开渠修荒滩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年丰收生活好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙河再不闹水淹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（汉口罗家庄）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}